{
  "name": "core.openwop.http",
  "kind": "node",
  "description": "HTTP + general transport pack. v1.0 baseline: core.openwop.http.fetch (retry, backoff, idempotency). v1.1 additions: openapi-call, GraphQL (query/mutation/subscription), SOAP, gRPC (4 streaming variants), SSE consume, WebSocket client, long-poll, upload (multipart + resumable), download stream, pagination decorators (cursor/offset/link-header), rate-limit-aware retry, circuit breaker, idempotency-key generator, webhook signature verifier (Stripe/GitHub/Slack/raw-hmac). Zero npm deps — Node 20+ fetch/undici; transports requiring native libs delegate to host capabilities.",
